OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSunil Perera: Sri Lanka's  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flarger than life music     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flegend dies at 68          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, His songs have pulled people on to     
OL,6, dance floors at weddings and parties   
OL,7, for decades.                           
OL,9,FSunil Perera, one of the stalwarts of  
OL,10,FSri Lanka's baila genre - a memento of 
OL,11,FPortuguese colonisation - died on      
OL,12,FMonday aged 68, his family said.       
OL,14,FHe is believed to have died of         
OL,15,FCovid-related complications.           
OL,17,FAlong with his band The Gypsies, Sunil 
OL,18,Fwrote and performed songs with catchy  
OL,19,Ftunes and clever lyrics, often about   
OL,20,FSri Lankan life and politics.          
